result.name: Matsubishi Japanese Restaurant

reviews.text: Highly skilled chef preparing food right in front of you, high entertaining value. Only quality ingredients used, food was delicious.

Amazing restaurant with amazing chefs. Everyone is very professional at all times yet friendly and pays attention to you.
The food is phenomenal and the chefs know all about it too if you ask them. Watching them cook is eye opening, their instruments are like extensions of their iwn arms. All food is prepared to a very high standard and it shows when you finally get to eat it. 
Portions are also surprisingly filling.

Food is cooked right in front of you and one chef is usually assigned to a group, therefore the food doesn't take long to get into your stomach!

10/10 would definitely come again.

Very grand and nice place for Teppanyaki food. The food is good and no doubt. I would suggest lunch set than the dinner compare by the price tag. BTW their place is good for friends gathering or the business meeting (private room)
Solid food, good service. Private rooms are great for business, but the public area is a bit smokey, remember to check your jacket before going in

Leading Japanese food here for several 10 years! Today I tried the teppanyaki set of $300 which comprises of seafood and beef plus rice or noodle and of course dessert of ice cream or pudding to finish. It was a fulfil lunch indeed. Situated in a known hotel is a plus as well as the panoramic sea view.

reviews.text: Clean and tidy
I go there every year to attend leather fair.. Love this place..
Exhibitions every weekdays and weekend, full of guests, exhibitors, promoters and scalpers. It's big with many storey, easy get lost.
Excellent products sold in the Design Gallery but the price is too high. Some items are much cheaper on Amazon.
Limited shops, at least there is a design gallery which shows products of HK and a HSBC bank...
夏は涼しく快適。観光地？ではないと思います。お土産とかも買えますが、その時は空港で十分だと思います。
灣仔區議會其中一個中檔次商场。
Barang barangnya keren". Banget
設計同交通都好
Clean and tidy
